        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Master's Student from India, £18k/year budget</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">1-year MSc at Manchester, living in student halls.</p>
        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">✓ NHS covers all health needs. Registered with campus GP, got flu jab free. Uses NHS for prescriptions (£9.90/item). No private insurance needed—healthy and manages fine.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
